item.title: CVE-2023-0062|2024-08-02T04:54:32.602Z -- unknown -- ean%20for%20woocommerce
item.description: The EAN for WooCommerce WordPress plugin before 4.4.3 does not validate and escape some of its shortcode attributes before outputting them back in a page/post where the shortcode is embed, which could allow users with the contributor role and above to perform Stored Cross-Site Scripting attacks.
